üîΩüéûÔ∏èDownloading videos in multiple smaller files Youtube-dl/yt-dlp + ffmpeg

youtube-dl -v "https://www.twitch.tv/videos/xxx" --hls-prefer-ffmpeg --external-downloader-args "-ss 00:30:00 -to 00:40:00"

